headline: GE HealthCare launches new advanced digital X-ray system to enable access and increase efficiency in high throughput settings
summary: CHICAGO, July 24, 2025--GE HealthCare (Nasdaq: GEHC), today announced commercial availability of an advanced floor-mounted digital X-ray system, Definium™ Pace Select ET1, designed to deliver high-image quality and optimize efficiency in highly demanding environments while enhancing access and affordability.
